When this took place the que was omitted for the scansion. This gives VU’s reading. In the other MSS ululare was corrupted to uolitare and then omitted as superfluous and un- metrical (in M without this excuse) and cunctas added to make a linel. The sense will be then ‘ they seemed to hear their fathers shriek like spirits of the dead and to see their bloody wraiths flit before their eyes.' sanguinis: ‘ sanguineas,' cf. 773 n.; it explains why the appearance was an omen scelerum. They hoped to slay their parents.
